snippet.title: GFL Station
snippet.description:
Welcome to The GFL Station! We are a team of 6 and we delight in bringing you channelled messages from The Galactic Federation of Light, bringing them to LIFE exclusively for YouTube using professional voice over artists and carefully selected artwork. We take hours working with our graphic artist and our channelers, making The GFL Station the most unique/exclusive hub for channeled messages on YouTube. Our 8 stage (!) process for making a video:

1) Build/write script from channeling message
2) Refine as needed and include voiceover notes
3) Send script to voiceover team
4) Record voiceover
5) Refine/amend/re-record as needed
6) Select/build visuals
7) Select & design thumbnail art
8) Post!

DISCLAIMER: All channeled messages are provided for entertainment purposes ONLY

Have a channelled message that you'd like us to bring to life? Send us a mail! 
gflstation@gmail.com

We are honoured to be of service,

GFL Team.
